question: Bengals vs. Colts
description:
In the upcoming NFL game, scheduled for December 10 at 1:00 PM ET:

If the Cincinnati Bengals win, the market will resolve to “Bengals”.

If the Indianapolis Colts win, the market will resolve to “Colts”.

 If the game is not completed by December 17, 2023 (11:59 PM ET) or it ends in a tie, the market will resolve 50-50.

question: All 3 University Presidents who testified on antisemitism out by Jan 31?
description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if it is announced all three presidents who testified on antisemitism have resigned or otherwise left their offices by Jan 31, 2024, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise this market will resolve to “ No.”

The presidents who count toward the resolution of this market are:
- Elizabeth "Liz" Magill of University of Pennsylvania
- Sally Kornbluth of Massachusetts Institute of Technology
- Claudine Gay of Harvard University

Note that announcements before the end date of their resignations count for this market’s resolution, regardless of when the resignations go into effect.
